Module kivakit.core.kernel

Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.data.validation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Validatable
    An object that is Validatable can create a Validator for a given kind of Validation.
    ValidationReporter
    Reporter of validation issues.
    Validator
    When Validator.validate(Listener) is called, a Validator validates itself, using the listener parameter to send messages like Problem s and Warnings as validation proceeds.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseValidationReporter
    Base implementation of validation reporter that reports any message it hears in BaseValidationReporter.onMessage(Message).
    Validation
    A kind of validation as restricted to a particular set of value types.
